	<div class="container promo-text">
		<div class="inner clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>World&#8209;Cup Malware: the Kick&#8209;Off</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Looking into their crystal balls (no jokes, please) at the end of 2009, our colleagues in Latin America came up with a prophecy that was later incorporated into a white paper (2010: Cybercrime Coming of Age): In June 2010, one of the most popular regular sports events, the soccer World Cup, will take place in</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
            </div>
    <span class="meta">
		<span class="strong">
			<time datetime="2010-03-26 09:06:39">26 Mar 2010 - 09:06AM</time>
		</span>
			</span>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>	

